00:23:18.860 --> 00:23:22.929
Julie Stout: And we moved out to Colorado.

156
00:23:23.420 --> 00:23:25.920
Julie Stout: Where my husband had a job.

157
00:23:26.040 --> 00:23:33.440
Julie Stout: In the steel industry, what he… that his family had been in. He was… he was American,

158
00:23:33.610 --> 00:23:36.419
Julie Stout: I was not supposed to marry an American.

159
00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:48.220
Julie Stout: And… Unfortunately, I had a beau who was Latvian, and the whole family loved him.

