177
00:25:32.000 --> 00:25:52.179
Julie Stout: And we lived there for 2 years, and the saying down there was that if you come from the outside, as we did, and there were some friends we made who had come from Tennessee, from California, and other places, if you come from outside, you're going to be here one year because you're so confused, you don't know what to do, and the second year, you know you're leaving.

178
00:25:52.270 --> 00:26:04.830
Julie Stout: And yet, even though, as I say that, we made so many friends. We just made so many friends in those two years. It was a very, very special place, very special place.

